Pre-Game Insights: The Ireland vs. South Africa ODI series begins on October 2, 2024, in Abu Dhabi, marking their first encounter in the UAE. South Africa leads the head-to-head 6-1 with Ireland's only win in 2021.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This will be the first ODI series in the UAE for both teams, with previous series ending 1-1. The last five matches show South Africa's dominance with three wins and one no result, while Ireland's only win was in 2021.
